Open the door full on.

1034
00:50:18,860 --> 00:50:19,980
Kicks the door open.

1035
00:50:21,259 --> 00:50:26,299
As the door opens, Thea turns and says,

1036
00:50:27,100 --> 00:50:38,700
Well, I want them to listen.

1037
00:50:38,700 --> 00:50:41,740
Nah, sometimes you just have to tie a person down

1038
00:50:41,740 --> 00:50:42,539
to make them listen.

1039
00:50:43,900 --> 00:50:47,100
So you guys have to make a wisdom saving throw

1040
00:50:47,100 --> 00:50:49,900
or be paralyzed and have to listen to my diatribe

1041
00:50:49,900 --> 00:50:50,300
for the duration.

1042
00:50:50,300 --> 00:50:52,380
I'm a lot more sympathetic to people

1043
00:50:52,380 --> 00:50:54,060
when they tie me up first.

1044
00:50:54,780 --> 00:50:55,340
Yeah.

1045
00:50:55,420 --> 00:50:56,300
Totally.

1046
00:50:56,300 --> 00:50:58,700
Hey, hey, they came out swinging first.

1047
00:50:58,700 --> 00:51:00,780
I have to also show that, you know.

1048
00:51:00,780 --> 00:51:02,940
I have advantage, so it was an 18.

1049
00:51:02,940 --> 00:51:03,180
I'm playing the game.

1050
00:51:03,180 --> 00:51:04,940
Oh, and an 11, so 18.

1051
00:51:04,940 --> 00:51:05,340
Same.

1052
00:51:05,340 --> 00:51:08,220
I rolled a four and a six, which puts me at a 19.

1053
00:51:09,100 --> 00:51:10,059
So like nothing happens.

1054
00:51:10,059 --> 00:51:11,500
I wiggle my fingers at you and I'm like...

1055
00:51:15,019 --> 00:51:15,660
That's what I say.

1056
00:51:16,780 --> 00:51:17,500
And then I say,

1057
00:51:18,300 --> 00:51:20,460
You don't think you know what you know.

1058
00:51:21,019 --> 00:51:21,500
I don't.

1059
00:51:22,140 --> 00:51:23,420
I don't know what that means.

1060
00:51:23,420 --> 00:51:24,539
What is she talking about?

1061
00:51:25,340 --> 00:51:26,220
I don't know either.

1062
00:51:26,220 --> 00:51:28,539
You speak in riddles, Thea.

1063
00:51:29,260 --> 00:51:30,300
Get to your point.

1064
00:51:30,300 --> 00:51:33,019
Is it intriguing enough to maybe take down the darkness?

1065
00:51:34,140 --> 00:51:35,420
Let us talk for a moment.

1066
00:51:35,420 --> 00:51:36,539
Do you have any liquor?

1067
00:51:36,539 --> 00:51:38,059
I mean, is the darkness even affecting you?

1068
00:51:38,059 --> 00:51:41,340
Because you literally just cast a spell on me, which...

1069
00:51:41,340 --> 00:51:41,740
Oh, no.

1070
00:51:41,740 --> 00:51:43,420
I mean, it's so scary.

1071
00:51:43,420 --> 00:51:44,700
It's very, very loud.

1072
00:51:44,700 --> 00:51:45,980
You can see me.

1073
00:51:45,980 --> 00:51:47,180
I can barely hear you.

1074
00:51:47,180 --> 00:51:48,700
You literally targeted me, so...

1075
00:51:48,700 --> 00:51:49,420
I can see you.

1076
00:51:49,420 --> 00:51:50,300
Fine.

1077
00:51:50,300 --> 00:51:51,019
No, I can see you.

1078
00:51:51,019 --> 00:51:51,579
You guys...

1079
00:51:51,579 --> 00:51:52,220
But tall gear, too.

1080
00:51:52,220 --> 00:51:52,940
All right.

1081
00:51:52,940 --> 00:51:53,260
Fine.

1082
00:51:53,820 --> 00:51:54,380
All right.

1083
00:51:54,380 --> 00:51:55,180
Just hear me out.

1084
00:51:55,180 --> 00:51:58,539
And then, you know, if we can keep fighting and I won't like,

1085
00:51:58,539 --> 00:52:00,140
you know, pull any shitty things on you,

1086
00:52:00,140 --> 00:52:01,260
like we'll just like full out,

1087
00:52:01,260 --> 00:52:03,579
like really give ourselves a run for our money.

1088
00:52:03,579 --> 00:52:03,900
Okay?

1089
00:52:04,539 --> 00:52:08,539
You saw what I did to Shamalama Bing Bong with this wand.

1090
00:52:09,340 --> 00:52:10,380
I mean, I didn't see it.

1091
00:52:11,180 --> 00:52:12,220
I don't know who you are.

1092
00:52:12,860 --> 00:52:13,740
I don't know who you are.

1093
00:52:13,740 --> 00:52:15,019
Oh, this is...

1094
00:52:15,019 --> 00:52:15,820
Okay, sorry.

1095
00:52:15,820 --> 00:52:16,780
Introductions.

1096
00:52:16,780 --> 00:52:17,340
Tall gear.

1097
00:52:17,900 --> 00:52:20,140
This is Vorunax and Lip Sinky.

1098
00:52:20,140 --> 00:52:20,940
I mean, I figured.

1099
00:52:21,820 --> 00:52:23,500
Well, but I mean like,

1100
00:52:23,500 --> 00:52:25,820
really, an introduction is necessary.

1101
00:52:25,820 --> 00:52:29,579
In their young years, they have accomplished so much.

1102
00:52:29,579 --> 00:52:30,940
Oh, I mean, well that's...

1103
00:52:30,940 --> 00:52:31,500
True.

1104
00:52:31,500 --> 00:52:32,139
That's...

1105
00:52:32,139 --> 00:52:36,860
We really have written the Orcus Corporate letter

1106
00:52:36,860 --> 00:52:37,739
right to the top.

1107
00:52:37,739 --> 00:52:38,780
Lip Sinky, hold it.

1108
00:52:38,780 --> 00:52:40,699
We are not roles to be buttered.

1109
00:52:40,699 --> 00:52:41,900
Oh, well...

1110
00:52:41,900 --> 00:52:43,820
Hey, I mean, who else butters your role?

1111
00:52:43,820 --> 00:52:45,500
Well, we've got a...

1112
00:52:45,500 --> 00:52:46,300
That's private.

1113
00:52:49,019 --> 00:52:50,539
Yeah, I mean, that's private.

1114
00:52:50,539 --> 00:52:52,699
That's what I was going to say, too.

1115
00:52:52,700 --> 00:52:54,460
You're a dirty birdie and I like it.

1116
00:52:54,460 --> 00:52:55,740
Okay, so about this liquor.

1117
00:52:55,740 --> 00:52:56,780
You've got any anywhere?

1118
00:52:58,140 --> 00:52:58,700
You know what?

1119
00:52:58,700 --> 00:53:01,420
And then, and Thea pulls out a wineskin

1120
00:53:01,420 --> 00:53:02,620
and takes a swig and is like,

1121
00:53:02,620 --> 00:53:04,700
anybody, this is going to be heavy, y'all.

1122
00:53:04,700 --> 00:53:05,980
This is going to be heavy.

1123
00:53:05,980 --> 00:53:08,540
Vorunax, you especially, like for you, for sure.

1124
00:53:08,540 --> 00:53:10,220
If it is as heavy as you say it is,

1125
00:53:10,940 --> 00:53:13,900
then I'd rather be in my right mind to understand it.

